      | v0.3.0  | 4     | Full UI shell (multi-pane dashboard + agent observability)                                                                                            |
      | v0.4.0  | 5     | Windows DPAPI hardening + release signing + auto-update                                                                                               |
      
      Each phase lives as a FID under `dev/fids/` as it ships.
      
