      ## What's in this repo
      
      | Path                       | Purpose                                                                                                    |
      | :------------------------- | :--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
      | `src-tauri/`               | Tauri 2 Rust daemon: master-key vault, OpenRouter client, IPC command surface                              |
