       * `{ status: "REJECTED", reason: "SEC_8_LIMIT_EXCEEDED" }` on the
       * server-side SEC #8 rejection. On success, the mock IPC also
       * persists the payload as the new swarm baseline (FID-013) so the
       * next `getSwarmBaseline` returns it.
