## Why "forcing the agent to output the structure destroyed the output"

The Markdown is the **cognitive substrate**. The agent thinks in prose, paragraphs, code blocks, philosophical asides. If you ask it to write JSON, it starts thinking in JSON syntax — it stops having thoughts and starts having schemas. The output becomes a list of fields instead of a mind. That's what broke the previous attempt. The agent's emergent writing was the value, not the data shape.

